instructions:
# Important Dates
- Submission deadline: September 24, 11:59PM, 2024
- Workshop: October 19 -- 20
# Submission format
- We recommend the [ICLR template](https://github.com/ICLR/Master-Template) for submission.
- Page limit is **one page** (at most two pages, approximately, 200 words).
# Topics
- Creation of LLMs, e.g., pre-training, finetuning, alignment, data acquisition and preparation;
- LLM deployment, e.g., efficiency, security, trustworthiness, safety, and privacy;
- LLM domain-specific applications, e.g., science, engineering, medicine, law, and health;
- LLM user experience, e.g., choice of models, service, data, frameworks, or workflow;
- LLMs in education and for education;
- Ethical issues in LLMs in scientific and engineering applications, e.g., bias and fairness.
